    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Updating the language from `C.UTF-8` to `en-US.UTF-8` fixes the issue.\r\n\r\n```\r\nLANG                           en_US.UTF-8\r\nLC_ALL                         en_US.UTF-8\r\n```\r\n\r\nLet me know if that works for you.",
